description: Entirely surrounded by a field of meadow grass, a small rectangular building squats in the moonlight, its wooden walls blackened by years of weathering and a lack of upkeep.  A faint sour smell, akin to swamp mud, emanates from behind a rickety wooden door.

Entirely surrounded by a field of meadow grass, a small rectangular building squats in the moonlight, its wooden walls blackened by years of weathering and a lack of upkeep.  The diminutive structure, sheltering no more than a single room, is undecorated, save for a tiny symbol carved atop the doorway.  A faint sour smell, akin to swamp mud, emanates from behind a rickety wooden door.
